 1995-20821995-12-120,  INT'L TRADE,  ,  , 
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of ROBERT G. WRIGHT, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Export Development Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective December 18, 1995, in the place of Robert Allen Kilpatrick.
